Introductory Russian II (RSSN1120)

Course level

Undergraduate

Faculty

Humanities and Social Sciences

School

Languages & Cultures School

Units

2

Duration

One Semester

Class contact

4 Contact hours

Incompatible

Senior Russian or equivalent

Prerequisite

RSSN1110

Assessment methods

Participation and attendance, weekly online homework and quizzes, discussion board, mid-semester and final oral exam, final written exam

Course coordinator

Dr Anna Mikhaylova

Study Abroad

This course is pre-approved for Study Abroad and Exchange students.
